  <zone type="main">
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e2-0076.01"/>
    <line rend="indent2">Asia</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0076.01"/>
    <line>Fit throne for such a power! Magnificent <unclear>:</unclear></line>
    <line>How glorious art thou Earth! &amp; if thou beest</line>
    <line>The shadow of some Spirit lovelier still</line>
    <line>Though evil stain its work and it <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">must</del>
        <add place="superlinear">should be</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">Like all we love</del>
        <mod>
          <del rend="strikethrough"><add place="superlinear">As <unclear>thou</unclear>
              perchance</add></del>
          <add place="superlinear">Like its creation</add>
        </mod>
      </mod>, weak <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">although</del>
        <add place="superlinear">yet</add>
      </mod> beautiful</line>
    <line>I could fall down &amp; worship that &amp; thee&#8212;</line>
    <line>Even now my heart adoreth&#8212;Wonderful!</line>
    <line>Look Sister &#8212; ere the vapour dim thy brain;</line>
    <line>Beneath is a wide plain of billowy mist</line>
    <line>As a lake, paving in the morning sky,</line>
    <line>With azure waves which burst in silver light</line>
    <line>Some Indian vale...behold it, rolling on</line>
    <line>Under the curdling winds, &amp; islanding</line>
    <line>The peak whereon we stand&#8212;midway, around</line>
    <line>Encinctured by the dark &amp; blooming forests</line>
    <line>Dim twilight lawns &amp; stream-illumed caves</line>
    <line>And wind-inchanted shapes of wandering mist</line>
    <line rend="indent1"><metamark function="count"><add place="intralinear">293</add></metamark>And
      far on high the keen sky-cleaving <anchor xml:id="e2-0076.03"/></line>
  </zone>
</surface>
